deck = Deck()
cards = Cards(max_count=7)
assert cards.size == 0
assert deck.size == 52
cards.pull(deck, 3)
assert cards.size == 3
assert deck.size == 49
cards.pull(deck, 2)
assert cards.size == 5
assert deck.size == 47
cards.pull(deck, 10)
assert cards.size == 7
assert deck.size == 45
cards.pull(deck, 5)
assert cards.size == 7
assert deck.size == 45
